  ^ <fb>^template(`quickreply`, `I'm done!`, `Have some questions.`, `Working on it.`)</fb>
  ^ <sms><send>If you need some assistance,\nText the letter A.\nIf you've finished (and can't be stopped!)\nText the letter B.\nIf you're still working on it,\nText the letter C.</sms>
  ^ {@ setvars}
  - Hey, <get username>!\n
  ^ How's progress on action item <get taskNum>?
  ^ <fb>^template(`quickreply`, `Finished!`, `Have some questions.`, `Working on it.`)</fb>
  ^ <sms><send>Have a few questions?\nText the letter A.\nAlready done?\nText the letter B.\nStill chipping away at it?\nText the letter C.</sms>
  ^ {@ setvars}
  - <get username>! Checking in. How are things going with action item <get taskNum>?
  ^ <fb>^template(`quickreply`,`Finished!`, `Have some questions.`, `Working on it.`)</fb>
  ^ <sms><send>Have questions?\nText the letter A.\nFinished?\nText the letter B.\nNot quite there yet?\nText the letter C.</sms>
  ^ {@ setvars}
  - Hi, <get username>! Hope you've been having a great day. How are things going with action item <get taskNum>?
  ^ <fb>^template(`quickreply`, `Finished!`, `Have some questions.`, `Working on it.`)</fb>
  ^ <sms><send>If you'd like my assistance,\nText the letter A.\nIf you're already done,\nText the letter B.\nIf you want me to check back later,\nText the letter C.</sms>
  ^ {@ setvars}
  - Greetings, <get username>! How's it going with action item <get taskNum>?
  ^ <fb>^template(`quickreply`, `Finished!`, `Have some questions.`, `Working on it.`)
  ^ <sms><send>If you'd like my assistance,\nText the letter A.\nIf you're already done,\nText the letter B.\nIf you want me to check back later,\nText the letter C.</sms>
  ^ {@ setvars}
  + (a|have some questions|need some assistance|yes i have questions)
  - {topic=help} {@ startprompt}
  + (b|working on it)
  - As Confucius said, "It does not matter how slowly you go as long as you do not stop."<send>
