  ^ ^template(`button`, `You're doing great! Let me know if you need any help!`, `{"A": "Need some assistance", "D": "No thanks. I'm good."}`) {@ setvars}
  - *Working on it* means you're getting it done! So, **hi five**!<send>
  ^ ^template(`button`, `You're doing great! Let me know if you need any help!`, `{"A": "Need some assistance", "D": "No thanks. I'm good."}`) {@ setvars}
